                attachments</span
              >
            </div>

            <div class="feature">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="feature-icon"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              <span
                >Automated renewal reminders keep your clients from churning</span
              >
            </div>

            <div class="feature">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="feature-icon"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              <span
                >Chat with clients directly in the app - no more missed phone
                calls</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="#" onclick="return false" class="cta-button disabled">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .solutions-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 1200px;
  }

  .solution-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .solution-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .app-card {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f7f9fc, #ffffff);
  }

  .solution-content {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .solution-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .solution-header h2 {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .app-preview {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .phone-icon {
    width: 4rem;
    height: 4rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .solution-description {
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .features-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #0d3f6b;
  } 

  .cta-button.disabled {
    background: #cccccc;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .beta-text {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .solutions-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .solution-card {
      margin: 0 1rem;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .phone-icon {
      width: 3rem;
      height: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
